{"tid":1470712,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 機場實施管制，只有持登機證才可進入","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:03:35.000Z","uid":273619,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"83a975890f2b30cfefb54545c979888479910c39","tid":1470712,"uid":273619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"機場通道實施管制<br />\n<br />\n機場一號客運大樓 2 及 3 號通道實施管制，只有持登機證的離境旅客才獲准進入。通道玻璃門上亦貼有法庭禁制令。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/715831998830066/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F715831998830066%2F&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=81118488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/715831998830066/</a>"},{"pid":"688ae28f9d92373bd5a8438e2db21aff2bdc556f","tid":1470712,"uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"on9，圍住個入口咪得。"},{"pid":"cac0b52b204c22fbde35d74e6688c9708775004a","tid":1470712,"uid":18061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"真係接機都唔撚比？"},{"pid":"2bad4290ea1115ab58b4f2c488ad106f21a1d7b7","tid":1470712,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"1號通道呢"},{"pid":"32fedd50902af422afe49d54d3ff2e07edb79640","tid":1470712,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474558-20190814.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR3em-OwN0qDc_e2fwFstoKAsBsbxy3ySBjHnSFSho6AzNNhYvu0IGyCTdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474558-20190814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR3em-OwN0qDc_e2fwFstoKAsBsbxy3ySBjHnSFSho6AzNNhYvu0IGyCTdI&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=b2c4be62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474558-20190814.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR3em-OwN0qDc_e2fwFstoKAsBsbxy3ySBjHnSFSho6AzNNhYvu0IGyCTdI&h=4f80c160\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474558-20190814.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR3em-OwN0qDc_e2fwFstoKAsBsbxy3ySBjHnSFSho6AzNNhYvu0IGyCTdI</a>"},{"pid":"a29d9932219fe50b7d504424c69680c59dfbe02c","tid":1470712,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"係時候舉紅旗了"},{"pid":"c799e0d7a0cb6917bf8e34dad5de8e788c88984b","tid":1470712,"uid":294052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"應該係送機唔比"},{"pid":"9639ed36952979b384745a2c7a3f1e1ac379ff15","tid":1470712,"uid":273619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"【機場即時】一號客運大樓加強保安 持登機證者方可進入<br />\n<br />\n機管局在連續兩日示威後推出新措施，只有持登機證旅客方可進入一號客運大樓離境層，變相擴大機場禁區範圍。現場所見大量路面出入口關閉，只剩少量開放供旅客出入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68373931_2395189463883069_2983292530138808320_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQmtKFbTd6bvwwit-OQFLQcRy9f4YdAVxeYp-EnpsnDy1U2y6GRE4UmZMMNFWlK49AQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=aa300fea80904e2735dae3fb3c8e7523&amp;oe=5DC824CD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68373931_2395189463883069_2983292530138808320_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQmtKFbTd6bvwwit-OQFLQcRy9f4YdAVxeYp-EnpsnDy1U2y6GRE4UmZMMNFWlK49AQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daa300fea80904e2735dae3fb3c8e7523%26oe%3D5DC824CD&h=8d8ca906&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65f235cb5bb87999716a8d64a933ed826ed7bde","tid":1470712,"uid":199227,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"圍入口一樣可以收佢地皮<br />\n最多熱啲"},{"pid":"c84207daaabfb49dff231d6f31de33a68e3507e3","tid":1470712,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,